<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idef865e53-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1994—<ref href="/us/pl/103/349">Pub. L. 103–349</ref> struck out “his” before “plant” in first sentence.</p>
